    • RECKON_QPOS_FIELD

      public static final java.lang.String RECKON_QPOS_FIELD
      reckon-queue-position Queue position used to calculate the estimated ready-date for an on-hold item. Of particular interest is the difference between the "reckon-queue-position" (start value for computing progress in queue position) and "check-queue-position" (end value for computing progress in queue position).
      See Also:
